      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Chris Hadkiss, Chief Executive, APHA, joined in January 2013.</p>

<p>His previous roles include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Home Office Advisor on Forensic Science</li>
  <li>Executive Director, Forensic Science Service Ltd</li>
  <li>Operations Director, Forensic Science Service Ltd</li>
  <li>Lead Regional Manager, Forensic Science Service Ltd</li>
</ul>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_2195">
            <h1 id="chief-executive">Chief Executive</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Chief Executive is responsible for the delivery of the agency’s services and is the ‘accounting officer’ for the budget. He is also an executive member of the Animal Health and Welfare Board for England.</p>
</div>
